rgb(0, 0, 0);" class=3D""><span class=3D"Apple-tab-span" =
style=3D"white-space:pre">	</span>=E2=80=A2 co-construction de =
crit=C3=A8res d'int=C3=A9r=C3=AAt (facettes) r=C3=A9pondant aux besoins =
de recherche et jusque-l=C3=A0 non exploit=C3=A9s dans les moteurs de =
recherche d=E2=80=99articles scientifiques ;<br =
class=3D""></span></font></div><div class=3D""><font color=3D"#000000" =
class=3D""><span style=3D"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class=3D""><span =
class=3D"Apple-tab-span" style=3D"white-space:pre">	</span>=E2=80=A2 =
mise au point de m=C3=A9thodes d=E2=80=99extraction de ces nouvelles =
facettes dans les articles scientifiques ;<br =
class=3D""></span></font></div><div class=3D""><font color=3D"#000000" =
class=3D""><span style=3D"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class=3D""><span =
